<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n09035e"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n09" href="#n09035e">N09 (VI.B.1)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n09all.htm#n09035e"> 35(e)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> <font face="wake">H</font> pipi <font color="green">[s&apos;]</font> metres / poudre de riz </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: Fr. <i>Faire pipi</i>, to pee. Fr. <i>Se mettre de la poudre de riz</i>, to put on rice powder (in popular cosmetic use). A French equivalent of the English euphemism &lsquo;to powder one&apos;s nose&rsquo; (to go to the lavatory). </mm> </dd></dl>
